snippet.title: Big Red Flags In Harry And Meghan's Relationship
snippet.description:
Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's journey from the early days of their relationship to their eventual "Megxit" from the royal family has been a rocky one. They claimed in that bombshell Oprah Winfrey interview in March 2021 that the royal family wasn't very welcoming to Markle, and that some fellow royals even brought up concerns about their son Archie's skin tone. Markle's mental health also reportedly suffered during her short stint as a royal. Many of the twists and turns in their story have been unpredictable, but there have also been some clear warning signs along the way. Here are the red flags in Harry and Meghan's relationship, revealed.
